{"tid":1232624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家千祈唔好執著係佔路上","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:36:04.000Z","uid":212509,"like":832,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a17ab5d4468c2baa5d93a347c8de7053e5ba1c","tid":1232624,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"雨革既經驗話比我地聽<br />\n佔路不單止無法成為示威者既籌碼<br />\n反而會因為妨礙民生而令政府本錢增加<br />\n<br />\n馬路從來都只係我地既戰場，而唔係陣地<br />\n我地既陣地係自己既屋企，因為屋企先係最合適我地休息既地方<br />\n就算真係要佔路，只要夠人多，基本上住港九新界任何一條街都隨時係我地手上<br />\n<br />\n大家而家要做既係休養生息，唔好放棄<br />\n我地已經傷到林鄭既皮<br />\n只要再刺入少少，就可以傷其筋骨<br />\n咁我地就真係贏"},{"pid":"ca61401871617c1e2f48fa534198e6477dfd3d5d","tid":1232624,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a049650d04604347edd8e478262c2e2393b6455a","tid":1232624,"uid":73200,"like":5,"dislike":147,"score":-142,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a023b5bf7d3446bdd75a8625a7067e4a3910b563","tid":1232624,"uid":166391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"077c4bbcea30d0262f3893544fbd01df327c5e8d","tid":1232624,"uid":2617,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"諗起都陰功 2次大遊行 一次開拖<br />\n先刺到佢既皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ef7959605b434c98139e1cc98799f034132d68","tid":1232624,"uid":254022,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"岩，而家策略應該係做好文宣，下星期300萬上街"},{"pid":"fbbe7b9fe03a0bf89337cf887f0583cdde63a958","tid":1232624,"uid":3571,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdfe2e96357b932a35fcaf57740c3334c219cbdf","tid":1232624,"uid":212509,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"大家諗下<br />\n612我地政府夠成功收復被佔道路<br />\n最後結果係點？<br />\n<br />\n道路從來都唔係最重要，除非好似612咁，搞到建制入唔到去開會"},{"pid":"3e965a11db19799febc946e796d0f2fb66d9158c","tid":1232624,"uid":5408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4b389f254d09c0d90433f6dbde5720babaf3134","tid":1232624,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bdfe2e96357b932a35fcaf57740c3334c219cbdf","tid":1232624,"uid":212509,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"大家諗下<br />\n612我地政府夠成功收復被佔道路<br />\n最後結果係點？<br />\n<br />\n道路從來都唔係最重要，除非好似612咁，搞到建制入唔到去開會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"唔係我地政府，本來想打 我地被佔 最後被全部擊退"},{"pid":"9e4caa90bda19be954c7f9778f916ee6c3649c10","tid":1232624,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b39a09fd3edfed2f978754518ad9cbbb681ac1c","tid":1232624,"uid":157938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5b536fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"3314796bc820a44610913ad7a447923f031873ff","tid":1232624,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d33dd9b94f16d70d56d21a253cbc29dbece01c1","tid":1232624,"uid":6026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7a17ab5d4468c2baa5d93a347c8de7053e5ba1c","tid":1232624,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"雨革既經驗話比我地聽<br />\n佔路不單止無法成為示威者既籌碼<br />\n反而會因為妨礙民生而令政府本錢增加<br />\n<br />\n馬路從來都只係我地既戰場，而唔係陣地<br />\n我地既陣地係自己既屋企，因為屋企先係最合適我地休息既地方<br />\n就算真係要佔路，只要夠人多，基本上住港九新界任何一條街都隨時係我地手上<br />\n<br />\n大家而家要做既係休養生息，唔好放棄<br />\n我地已經傷到林鄭既皮<br />\n只要再刺入少少，就可以傷其筋骨<br />\n咁我地就真係贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"說好的不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eee311a7326f31ffc7f3affb48e381f1eab88c","tid":1232624,"uid":69013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"大家要冷靜<br />\n用智慧去解決問題"},{"pid":"18f92cd3e93881e97cbfa4ef617956d65dd49f1a","tid":1232624,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a049650d04604347edd8e478262c2e2393b6455a","tid":1232624,"uid":73200,"like":5,"dislike":147,"score":-142,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJ2vnhn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJ2vnhn.png&h=699a470a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMYKrJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t